---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="ARBE Project – Algorithmic Resource‑Based Economy">
  <section
    style="
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 3fr) minmax(0, 2.4fr);
      gap: 2.4rem;
      align-items: center;
    "
  >
    <div>
      <div
        style="
          display: inline-flex;
          align-items: center;
          gap: 0.5rem;
          padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
          border-radius: 999px;
          border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.4);
          background: radial-gradient(circle at top, rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.9), #020617);
          margin-bottom: 1.4rem;
          font-size: 0.75rem;
        "
      >
        <span
          style="
            width: 9px;
            height: 9px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: #22c55e;
            box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.9);
          "
        />
        <span>Research proposal – AMN sovereign digital currency</span>
      </div>

      <h1
        style="
          font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 3vw + 1.6rem, 3.4rem);
          line-height: 1.05;
          letter-spacing: -0.03em;
          margin: 0 0 1rem;
        "
      >
        From debt‑based money<br />to a resource‑aligned economy.
      </h1>

      <p
        style="
          max-width: 38rem;
          color: #9ca3af;
          font-size: 0.98rem;
          line-height: 1.6;
          margin-bottom: 1.4rem;
        "
      >
        ARBE (Algorithmic Resource‑Based Economy) and the AMN sovereign digital currency
        propose a new monetary framework: public, auditable and algorithmically governed,
        where money is no longer a tool of debt and control, but a neutral medium to
        exchange human work and real resources.
      </p>

      <div
        style="
          display: flex;
          flex-wrap: wrap;
          gap: 0.9rem;
          margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
        "
      >
        <a
          href="/whitepaper"
          style="
            padding: 0.65rem 1.3rem;
            border-radius: 999px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.5);
            background: linear-gradient(
              to right,
              rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.18),
              rgba(129, 140, 248, 0.16)
            );
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 500;
          "
        >
          Read the whitepaper
        </a>
        <a
          href="/docs"
          style="
            padding: 0.65rem 1.3rem;
            border-radius: 999px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.5);
            background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.9);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #e5e7eb;
          "
        >
          Overview & motivation
        </a>
      </div>

      <div
        style="
          display: grid;
          grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
          gap: 0.9rem;
          max-width: 32rem;
          font-size: 0.78rem;
          color: #9ca3af;
        "
      >
        <div>
          <div style="font-weight: 600; color: #e5e7eb; margin-bottom: 0.15rem;">
            Monetary stability
          </div>
          <div>Algorithmic PID controller targeting structural inflation ≈ 0.</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div style="font-weight: 600; color: #e5e7eb; margin-bottom: 0.15rem;">
            Resource‑anchored
          </div>
          <div>
            Money supply linked to real, measurable resources and productive capacity.
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div style="font-weight: 600; color: #e5e7eb; margin-bottom: 0.15rem;">
            Public & auditable
          </div>
          <div>
            Open, sovereign ledger with cryptographic audit of every monetary action.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div
      style="
        border-radius: 24px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.45);
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.16), transparent 55%),
          radial-gradient(circle at bottom, rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.2), #020617);
        padding: 1.4rem 1.5rem 1.6rem;
        box-shadow:
          0 24px 70px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.9),
          0 0 0 1px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.9);
      "
    >
      <h2
        style="
          font-size: 1rem;
          letter-spacing: 0.14em;
          text-transform: uppercase;
          color: #e5e7eb;
          margin-top: 0;
          margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
        "
      >
        ARBE Stack
      </h2>
      <div
        style="
          display: grid;
          grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.4fr) minmax(0, 1.2fr);
          gap: 1.1rem;
          font-size: 0.8rem;
          color: #e5e7eb;
        "
      >
        <div
          style="
            border-radius: 16px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.45);
            padding: 0.9rem;
            background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.95);
          "
        >
          <div style="font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.45rem;">Monetary core</div>
          <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 1.1rem; color: #9ca3af;">
            <li>AMN – sovereign digital unit of account</li>
            <li>PID‑based monetary controller u(t)</li>
            <li>Public, read‑only parameters Kₚ, Kᵢ, Kd</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div
          style="
            border-radius: 16px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.45);
            padding: 0.9rem;
            background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.9);
          "
        >
          <div style="font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.45rem;">Data & resources</div>
          <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 1.1rem; color: #9ca3af;">
            <li>RTM – Resource Token Model</li>
            <li>h(S(t)) &amp; Φ(Q(t)) functions</li>
            <li>Certified sensors &amp; resource feeds</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div
          style="
            border-radius: 16px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.45);
            padding: 0.9rem;
            background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.92);
          "
        >
          <div style="font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.45rem;">Ledger & governance</div>
          <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 1.1rem; color: #9ca3af;">
            <li>SLP – Sovereign Ledger Protocol</li>
            <li>AMA – Algorithmic Monetary Authority</li>
            <li>Multi‑layer, anti‑capture governance</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div
          style="
            border-radius: 16px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.6);
            padding: 0.9rem;
            background: linear-gradient(
              to bottom right,
              rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.2),
              rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.96)
            );
          "
        >
          <div style="font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.45rem;">Purpose</div>
          <p style="margin: 0; color: #e5e7eb;">
            Transform money from a mechanism of debt and control into what it should have
            always been: a transparent, stable and just medium to exchange human work and
            coordinate real resources.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
